strategies: I simply did my best to pay attention and learn the names of the cities. Some were instantaneously familiar to me; I have heard of them

memorable: Have I heard of this before? Does it seem at all similar to places I've certainly heard of?
unique: Is it familiar? Is it novel/unique? Is it the name of an already existing object? Does it seem a little strange?
